mize time on high-value activities.\nDrive the full hunt-to-close lifecycle with disciplined pipeline hygiene, consultative selling, and consistent 3x–4x coverage to ensure predictable revenue.\nCreate high-conversion scripts, battlecards, and A/B-tested outreach across multiple channels; align closely with marketing to fuel inbound opportunities.\nDeliver real-time visibility into revenue, identify conversion bottlenecks, and implement rapid-response tactics to maintain forecast accuracy.\n\nWho You Are:\n\n4–7 years of high-performance sales experience (SaaS, FinTech, or AI-services preferred).\nProven experience using AI tools (e.g., Clay, Apollo, Jasper, Gong, or ChatGPT) to augment sales workflows.\nDemonstrable history of hitting and exceeding personal quotas of $1M+ ARR.\nDeep proficiency in CRM (Salesforce/HubSpot) and the ability to build automated sequences.\n\nWhy You'll Love Working at Nysonian:\n\nCompetitive base salary.\nCollaborate with high-performing teams across fast-growing global brands.\nMeaningful opportunities for growth, ownership, and impact.\nA culture built on accountability, transparency, and execution.\n\nOur Commitment:\nNysonian is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees. We do not discriminate based on race, color, religion, sex (including pregnancy, gender identity, and sexual orientation), national origin, age, veteran status, disability, or any other legally protected characteristic. Reasonable accommodations are provided for applicants with disabilities."}
