sing → retention).​\n* Strong, systems-driven mindset: KPIs, dashboards, clean reporting, and discipline.​\n* Comfortable leading across Sales, Marketing, Ops, and CX without micromanaging.\n* Thrives in high-accountability environments and wants true ownership of revenue.​\n* Clear English communication and ability to work on U.S. Eastern Time.​\n\nTools you will oversee: GoHighLevel (CRM & automations), ClickUp (execution), marketing reports, and AI call coaching/analytics tools.​\n\n*Compensation & Growth*\n\n* *This is a remote role for US based company*\n* Competitive base salary + meaningful performance-based upside.​\n* Compensation linked to company growth and revenue performance.​\n* Long-term leadership trajectory with growing authority and market expansion opportunities.​\n\nThis role require working in US Eastern time zone.\n\nJob Type: Contract\nContract length: 12 months\n\nPay: Up to AED7,000.00 per month"}
