{"source":"linkedin","source_id":"4376723960","title":"Account Executive - Middle East","company":"Nebius","location":"Amsterdam","remote":false,"salary":"","posted_at":"","url":"","description":"Why work at NebiusNebius is leading a new era in cloud computing to serve the global AI economy. We create the tools and resources our customers need to solve real-world challenges and transform industries, without massive infrastructure costs or the need to build large in-house AI/ML teams. Our employees work at the cutting edge of AI cloud infrastructure alongside some of the most experienced and innovative leaders and engineers in the field.Where we workHeadquartered in Amsterdam and listed on Nasdaq, Nebius has a global footprint with R&amp;D hubs across Europe, North America, and Israel. The team of over 800 employees includes more than 400 highly skilled engineers with deep expertise across hardware and software engineering, as well as an in-house AI R&amp;D team.The role Nebius is hiring for a driven Account Executive - Middle East &amp; Africa￼ MEA marketplace. Targeting AI workloads across a set of industries and AI-native new logos and existing customers. Based in MEA you will manage strategic client relationships, uncover new business opportunities, work with partners and lead the end-to-end sales process—from initial engagement to closing. Your ability to understand complex business needs, craft tailored solutions, and thrive in a fast-moving, innovative environment will be key to your success. This role requires a solid blend of consultative selling, strategic thinking, and execution excellence to help clients unlock the full value of our platform.Our Sales team offers a fantastic opportunity to join a collaborative and supportive environment, where teamwork is just as valued as individual goals. You’ll have the chance to work with cutting-edge technology, while benefiting from a competitive commission structure. Working side-by-side with seasoned technology sa