{"source":"linkedin","source_id":"4376471821","title":"Head of Sales, IgniteTech (Remote) - $100,000/year USD","company":"Crossover","location":"Austin","remote":false,"salary":"","posted_at":"","url":"","description":"Sales operations today face widespread inefficiency, yet the potential for disruption remains significant. IgniteTech is fundamentally reshaping the sales function through advanced AI technologies that deliver measurable transformation. Our approach combines AI-enhanced execution with predictive forecasting capabilities to substantially improve both sales efficiency and effectiveness.This position centers on applying state-of-the-art generative AI to enhance real-time sales execution and guide strategic market forecasting. You will deploy AI systems that deliver immediate, actionable insights during live customer engagements and utilize forecasting models capable of anticipating market movements with exceptional precision. Your contributions will directly impact sales conversion rates and forecast accuracy, with systems that adapt continuously as market conditions change.You will join a team where your initiatives influence the broader business direction. Daily responsibilities include using AI to optimize existing sales workflows and communicating sophisticated AI capabilities to stakeholders without technical backgrounds. This role is designed for professionals who excel under demanding conditions, embrace complex challenges, and seek to advance the intersection of AI and sales.If driving transformative projects of this nature appeals to you, IgniteTech offers the platform. This is an opportunity to create meaningful impact by spearheading AI-powered sales innovation. If you are prepared to shape the future of B2B sales through pioneering AI applications, submit your application and help establish new benchmarks at IgniteTech.NOTE: Candidates receiving interview invitations are expected to complete comprehensive research on IgniteTech's products and